item.title: Game for boys for 6-7 years
item.description: The action of this game for boys for 6 7 years is developed in the water park. Here we decided to arrange a race on inflatable circles. Your character must not only quickly slide, but also perform all sorts of somersaults, jumps with a subfold, and so on. In a word, you need to score points by tricks and knocking out all the beachgoers you meet on the way. However, do not forget that during the passage of this game for boys, the hero can fly off the track himself.
